\id TIT - Nchane
\h Taytu
\toc1 Ŋwa wù Bol gɛ̀ saŋ fɛ Taytu le
\toc2 Taytu
\toc3 Tay
\mt1 Ŋwa wù Bol gɛ̀ saŋ fɛ Taytu le
\imt1 Fiɛɛ fì le a Ŋwa wu Taytu wunɛ le
\ip Ŋwa wunɛ gɛ̀ saŋ Bol fɛ chumu wumu le ba tɛŋe lɛ Taytu. Taytu gɛ̀ bee muh wù kituŋ kimi nyume gɛ ki Bajuu gɛ, wu gɛ̀ chinɛ kinche ki woŋ wuboo le wu kaasɛ wu tu nyu muh wu mbɛmɛ wu Kletu. Wu gɛ̀ lɛne bɛ Bol, nyu muh wù gɛ̀ fiih wu yi lɛme che chi jɛ yi Nyo le. Bol gɛ̀ saŋ ŋwa wunɛ fɛ chumu wunɛ le wu gɛ̀ bee woŋ wu Klɛt le. Wu gɛ̀ bee yo Bol chinɛ wu le lɛ wu shɛ̂ɛ wu fîih yo wu jîiŋe no lɛme chi kintaashɛ ki bamii ba mbɛmɛ gɛɛne.
\ip Bol taŋ Taytu kune kiŋge ki bamii ba le bikwɛɛ bi kintaashɛ ki bamii ba mbɛmɛ kɛme kì bo kɛme. Wu gɛ̀ jɛme wu le no wu gɛ̀ yɛde bamii ba Klɛt ba duude kɛme kiŋge nyume kì befe. Wu ka wu tefɛ Taytu no taŋlo wu yɛ̂yi bamii yeye yeye a kintaashɛ ki bamii ba mbɛmɛ le.
\iot Bikwɛɛ bi mwɛɛ mù le a Ŋwa wunɛ le
\io1 1:1-4 Fɛŋkɛɛ
\io1 1:5-16 Kune Bikwɛɛ bi kintaashɛ ki bamii ba mbɛmɛ
\io1 2:1-15 Kune gee chì bamii kɛme yeye yeye antɛnɛɛ a kintaashɛ ki bamii ba mbɛmɛ
\io1 3:1-11 Bol sɛɛŋ Taytu fiɛɛ fì wu kɛme ki wu yɛ̂yi bamii ba mbɛmɛ yu bachii
\io1 3:12-15 Kimɛsɛ
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Le mɛ wù Bol, nle mwa lɛme wu Nyo mo mwa ntuŋ wu Jiso Kletu. Lɛme chaŋ le ki ŋgêe mbɛmɛ wu bamii ba Nyo gɛ̀ cha wu gɛɛne fwe, bɛ lɛ bo kêe fiɛɛ fì nchiɛɛŋ fì bii kinche ki Nyo le,
\v 2 bo mo bo jîiŋe fwe yi kinche kì kage gɛ le. Kinche kinɛ le kì Nyo wù taŋlo wu gɛ mbiaŋ chimbiaŋ gɛ gɛ̀ ka fɛ woŋ kɛ.
\v 3 Kife kì chuule gɛ̀ doo ki kojɛ wu mo wu chunyɛ jɛ ye waaŋ fede yi jɛ ye yì nfeeji le. Gɛ̀ nya Nyo wù Mbvusɛ wese besabɛŋ bvuŋga bvuyu lɛ nfêeji.
\p 
\v 4 Nsaŋe ŋwa wunɛ fɛ wo le Taytu. Wo le mwa yaŋ wù nchiɛɛŋ yi mbɛmɛ wù le wese besabɛŋ le bachii. Nyo wù Chii bɛ Kletu Jiso wù le Mbvusɛ dûnyɛ besabɛŋ fitele fi joŋe wu ka wu nyâ bee bɛ nyiɛgee.
\s1 Lɛme chì Taytu gɛ̀ shɛshɛ Klɛt ki wu gê
\p 
\v 5 Fishaŋ fì ŋgɛ̀ shɛshɛ wo Klɛt gɛ̀ bee lɛ wo shɛɛ wo nâjɛ mwɛɛ mù gɛ̀ baaŋ mu nyume mu lɛnɛ, wo ka wo gɛ̂ɛ bachiji bintaashɛ bi bamii ba mbɛmɛ a bilaantɛŋ le bichii a je yì ŋgɛ̀ yɛyi wo yu le.
\v 6 Ki muh nyume chiji kintaashɛ tu wu kɛme ki wu nyûme muh wù ba kɛme gɛ fiɛɛ fì ba bɛɛme wu yi fi le gɛ. Wu kɛme ki wu nyûme juma kwɛse wu mumwaa, booŋ be nyume bamii ba mbɛmɛ, nyume gɛ wù bamii yɛne lɛ bo kuule lo kɛnɛ bo tɛɛme bikwɛɛ gɛ.
\v 7 No chiji kikwɛɛ ki kintaashɛ le muh wu lɛme wu Nyo, tu gɛ wu kɛme ki wu kɛ̂me fiɛɛ fì ba bɛɛme wu yi fi le gɛ. Gɛ wu kɛme ki wu nyûme muh wù tɛɛnyi kintɛɛnyɛ gɛ, kɛnɛ wù kɛme fitele fì saase gɛ, kɛnɛ muh wù muu mbvuuŋ mo koode wu gɛ. Gɛ wu kɛme ki wu nyûme muh wù wamɛ bamii kɛnɛ wù kuŋe gɛh nyume mbe wù achiji gɛ.
\v 8 Wu kɛme ki wu nyûme wu fii bamii ba jiɛnyi, wu koŋe fiɛɛ fì joŋe, wu shee bɛ ye ye, wu kɛme kinche kì chaaŋ, wu kɛme kinche kì yuude, wu kee no wu jiji ye ye le.
\v 9 Wu kɛme ki wu jîji n'yɛyɛ wù kooji le wù ba yɛyi wu yu chuule. Noo wu mo wu kɛɛ ki wu nyâa nteefɛ bamii le wù bii n'yɛyɛ wù kooji le, wu ka chiɛɛyi tɛ bamii ba tɛɛnyi n'yɛyɛ wuyu le.
\s1 Bo chîde n'yɛyɛ wu bamii ba chimbiaŋ
\p 
\v 10 Njɛme nɛ nje bamii le yu wesee bò tɛɛme bikwɛɛ, bo jɛme jɛ́ yì achiji, bo lɛɛde bɛ bamii, fede munchii ŋgoo yi bamii baa bò lɛme gɛh lɛ, ba kɛme ki ba chvûse bamii yeh.
\v 11 Bo banɛ le bamii ba bo bâŋ lo de yiboo, nje bo jiɛnyi bo chɛŋe bɛ yéh yi bamii yichii no bo yɛyi mwɛɛ mù bo kɛme gɛ ki bo yɛyɛ gɛ. Bo gee noo nje mbe wù achiji wù bo kuŋe.
\v 12 Bamii banɛ le muh wuboo wumu kibɛɛ wu to wu yɛne mwɛɛ le wu gɛ̀ jɛmɛ wa kune bo lɛ, “Bamii ba Klɛt to bo nyume bamii ba chimbiaŋ segechii. Bo le lo nyáŋ yi nchvuuŋ yì befe, nyume bawɛɛlɛ ba wude gɛh nyume mwɛɛ munjile.”
\v 13 Njɛmɛ wuyu wunɛ kune bo le nchiɛɛŋ. Noo, wo chîɛɛyi lo de yiboo le, wu lɛ bo kɛ̂me mbɛmɛ nyume wù kooji,
\v 14 fede ki bo nya bikwɛɛ biboo ki bo yuge nyume a baŋgaŋ ba Bajuu le, kɛnɛ mwɛɛ mù bamii ba le ba faŋ kinchiɛɛŋ kì Nyo duu lɛ bamii bîi ki le.
\v 15 Sege bamii kɛme muntele mù yuude, mwɛɛ munchii mo mu yuude fɛ bo le. Geenɛ, bo nɛ kɛme muntele mù yiide njɛ bo kɛme mbɛmɛ sɛŋ, fiɛɛ gɛ ka fi nyume yu fì yuude fɛ bo le gɛ, nje baŋkwajɛ baboo bɛ je yì muntele muboo le yu, le yi chɛŋe wa.
\v 16 Bobaa bamii jɛme lɛ bo kee Nyo, geenɛ gee chiboo ka chi duunyi lɛ bo le bo faŋ Nyo. Kinche kiboo nyiɛne baaŋ, bo tɛɛme bikwɛɛ. Gɛ bo nyume bamii bo taŋlo bo ge fiɛɛ fì joŋe gɛ.
\c 2
\s1 Ban'yɛyɛ kune kinche kì joŋe
\p 
\v 1 Fɛ wo le Taytu, fiuŋ le lɛ wo kɛme ki wo yɛ̂yi bamii nyume bɛ mwɛɛ mù chɛŋse a n'yɛyɛ wù kooji le.
\v 2 Wo têefe bilɛŋsɛ ba le wa ŋgamii lɛ bo jîji ye yiboo le yi fiɛɛ le fichii, bo kɛ̂me ŋgvunɛ fɛ bikwɛɛ biboo le, bo shêe bɛ ye yiboo, bo kɛ̂me mbɛmɛ nyume wù kooji, bo kɛ̂me kiŋkoŋɛ nyume kì kooji, bo kâane shɛ́ŋ yi baŋgɛ le bachii.
\p 
\v 3 Wo têefe tɛ bikɛse ba le wa ŋgamii, lɛ bo kɛ̂me kiŋge nyume kì duunyi ŋgvunɛ fɛ Nyo le. Keefɛ bo chɛ̂ŋe bɛ ajee a bamii gɛ. Keefɛ bo nyûme nfa yi mbvuuŋ gɛ. Bo yɛ̂yi bamii nyume bɛ mwɛɛ mù njoŋe.
\p 
\v 4 Noo, bo mo bo teefe ŋgóoŋ yi bikɛse no taŋlo bo kôŋe bilɛɛŋ baboo mo booŋ baboo,
\v 5 bo ka bo gêe mwɛɛ njɛ bamii ba shee bɛ bikwɛɛ biboo, bo chêe kinche kì yuude, bo lɛne chilɛme yéh yiboo le, bo kɛ̂me muntele mù njoŋe fɛ bamii le, bo yûge bilɛɛŋ baboo le. Noo, muh gɛ ka wu nyu yu wù taŋlo wu jɛme jɛ yì befe kune jɛ yi Nyo gɛ.
\p 
\v 6 Le gɛh yɛɛŋyɛɛŋ no wo lé wo jɛ̂me chú yi bamii le lɛ bo kɛme ki bo gêe mwɛɛ njɛ bamii ba kɛme bvufee.
\v 7 Wo dûunyi kiŋge kì joŋe yi fiɛɛ le fichii fì wo gee le, wu lɛ bamii yɛ̂ne bo bege. Sege wo yɛyi bamii bɛ fiɛɛ, wo lêesɛ fitele fiuŋ fichii yi fi le, wo yɛ̂yi bɛ fitele fiuŋ fichii,
\v 8 njɛmɛ wo nyume wù kooji wù taŋlo muh gɛ kɛmɛ fiɛɛ fì befe ki wu jɛ̂mɛ yo antɛnɛɛ gɛ. Noo, bamii ba kintɛɛnyɛ buŋ, bvuya le bvu koo bo nje gɛ bo kɛme fiɛɛ fì befe ki bo jɛme kune besabɛŋ gɛ.
\p 
\v 9 Wo têefe nfa lɛ bo nyâ bikwɛɛ biboo bamii ba kɛme bo le, bo gêe fiɛɛ fichii no bo goone lɛ bo gêe. Keefɛ bo chvûse fiɛɛ de yiboo le gɛ.
\v 10 Keefɛ bo chôŋe mwɛɛ muboo gɛ. Bo kɛme ki bo chûunyi lo jé le yichii lɛ bo le bamii ba nchiɛɛŋ. Nɛ bo gee noo yi fiɛɛ le fichii, bamii mo bo yɛde n'yɛyɛ wù kune Nyo wù le Mbvusɛ wese besabɛŋ, lɛ le fiɛɛ fì kɛme njoŋ.
\p 
\v 11 Wo yɛ̂yi bo noo, nje kiŋkoŋɛ ki Nyo le ki to wa wu lɛ taŋlo bamii bachii to bo bonɛ.
\v 12 Ki yɛyi besabɛŋ lɛ besabɛŋ chînɛ kinche kì Nyo koŋe gɛ le, bɛ lɛ keefɛ besabɛŋ kɛ̂me kiŋkoŋɛ kì baaŋ yi mwɛɛ mu yi nshɛŋ le gɛ. Lɛ besabɛŋ chêe bɛ bvufee bwesa besabɛŋ fo bvuchii, bee chêe kinche kì chaaŋ mo kinche kì Nyo goone yi woŋ kfunɛ le.
\v 13 Lɛ besabɛŋ chêe noo, bee chiɛɛne bvujoŋɛ bvù besabɛŋ jiiŋe fwe yi bvu le, bvu nyume bvu ge bvu bunɛ, bvù le bvukugɛ bvu Nyo wese besabɛŋ wù baaŋ wù le Mbvusɛ wù le Jiso Kletu.
\v 14 Wu gɛ̀ nya kikwɛɛ ke nje besabɛŋ ki wu sûuŋ bee yi bimbefɛ le bichii, ki wu gê besabɛŋ yuude, bee nyume bamii be ba kɛme kiŋkoŋɛ kì baaŋ kì bo gee gee chì joŋe.
\p 
\v 15 Munɛ le mwɛɛ mù wo kɛme ki wo yɛ̂yi bamii yu. Wo yûfe muntele muboo, wo nâji bo bɛ bvuŋga bvuchii bvù wo kɛme. Keefɛ wo bɛ̂ɛŋ muh laase wo gɛ.
\c 3
\s1 No taŋlo bamii ba mbɛmɛ gêe bɛ bamii bamu
\p 
\v 1 Wo tâne bamii ba mbɛmɛ lɛ bo yûge bamii ba sage woŋ le bɛ ba kɛme bvuŋga a bo we. Bo gêe fiɛɛ fì bo jɛme, bo nyûme bo seesɛ ki bo gee fiɛɛ fichii nyume fì kooji.
\v 2 Keefɛ bo jɛ̂me fiɛɛ fì befe kune muh gɛ. Keefɛ bo wâade waa gɛ. Bo nyûme nyiɛgee, bo jôde bikwɛɛ biboo fɛkuu a bamii bachii fwe.
\v 3 Wo kwâji lɛ besabɛŋ gɛ̀ shee tɛ bee gee kiyuŋ, bee tɛɛme bikwɛɛ, bamii lɛɛde bɛ bee bee jiaade je. Besabɛŋ gɛ̀ bee nfa yi mwɛɛ yeye yeye mù ye yese besebɛŋ koŋe, bee ka jii bikwɛɛ biɛsa. Besabɛŋ gɛ̀ chee kinche kesa bee kɛme gɛh nyume muntele mù mbefe bɛ kindoŋ kì bɛnɛ, bamii banɛ besabɛŋ, besabɛŋ banɛ tɛ bamii.
\p 
\v 4 Geenɛ, sege Nyo wù le Mbvusɛ wese besabɛŋ gɛ̀ dunyɛ bvujoŋɛ bwe bɛ kiŋkoŋɛ ke fɛ besabɛŋ le,
\v 5 wu mo wu bvusɛ besabɛŋ. Gɛ wu gɛ̀ bvuse besabɛŋ nje fiɛɛ fimi fì kooji fì besabɛŋ gɛ̀ ge le gɛ. Wu gɛ̀ bvuse nje yii ye, fede yi nchugɛ wu wù gɛ̀ chugɛ besabɛŋ le, besabɛŋ kɛmɛ boyɛ chì fɛŋ, Kiyo ki Yuude kusɛ besabɛŋ, besabɛŋ mo be nyume bamii bafɛŋ.
\v 6 Kiyo ki Yuude kinɛ le Nyo gɛ̀ chvu lo yi ye yese besabɛŋ le fede yi Jiso Kletu wù le Mbvusɛ wese besabɛŋ le.
\v 7 Wu gɛ̀ ge noo wu lɛ wu jô besabɛŋ lɛ besabɛŋ kɛme gɛ jialɛ gɛ, nje kiŋkoŋɛ ke fɛ bee le. Noo bee mo be nyume banji la be ba jiiŋe fwe ki be ge be kɛ̂mɛ kinche kì kage gɛ.
\v 8 Njɛmɛ wù njɛme wunɛ le lo nchiɛɛŋ.
\p Ŋgoone lɛ wo jɛ̂me wo chiise lo mwɛɛ munɛ bamii le, wu lɛ bamii ba bɛɛŋ Nyo le bo yɛŋ lɛ bo le bo nyâ bikwɛɛ biboo ki bo gee gee chì joŋe. Munɛ le mwɛɛ mù njoŋe baaŋ, mu too bɛ maajɛ fɛ bamii le bachii.
\v 9 Geenɛ, wo wɛ̂ɛne lo bɛ bambejɛ ba kiyuŋ, bɛ ajee a bachiji chikfuu chì bamii too bo taŋe. Wo wɛ̂ɛne tɛ bɛ kintɛɛnyɛ bɛ waa kune banchi ba Bajuu. Gɛ munɛ mwɛɛ kɛme lo maajɛ gɛ. Le mwɛɛ mù achiji.
\v 10 Nɛ muh le yu wù too bɛ kiŋgaye, wo jɛ̂mɛ wu le. Nɛ wo le wo jɛmɛ wu le chikɛ chimimia bu chikɛ chifɛɛ njɛ wu lu sɛŋ, wo chinɛ je ye le.
\v 11 Wo kêe lɛ wɛɛ muh le wu chinɛ wa je yì kooji le wu tu wu njiine lo, kinche ke le ki kimbefɛ, wu leesɛ wa kikwɛɛ ke yi ŋgɛ le.
\s1 Njɛmɛ wù kimɛsɛ bɛ ban'yɛsɛ
\p 
\v 12 Nlé ŋgê nchiiŋsɛ Atɛma kɛnɛ Tichiku fɛ wo le. Wu doo wu to, wo moŋ chuule ki wo tô fɛ mɛne Nikobole yanɛ. Le yo a nle nseesɛ lɛ nlé ŋgê nyûme yo yi kife ki nfuŋ wù tɛɛme le.
\v 13 Môŋ chuule ki wo fîh Sena muh wù kee banchi chuule, bɛ Abolo yi njiɛnyɛ wuboo le. Môŋ ki wo yɛ̂ŋ lɛ bo kɛmɛ fiɛɛ fichii fì bo goone.
\v 14 Bamii besa tɛ kɛme ki bo yɛyɛ ki bo nyâ bikwɛɛ biboo ki bo gêe chilɛme chì joŋe, wu lɛ taŋlo bo fîih yi mwɛɛ mù bo kɛme ki bo fîih le. Keefɛ bo nyûme gɛh lo achiji gɛ.
\p 
\v 15 Bamii bachii ba le fɛnɛ besa bo chiiŋse n'yɛsɛ wo le. Yɛ̂sɛ bamii bachii ba koŋe bee yi mbɛmɛ le. Tada dûnyɛ fitele fì joŋe fɛ bɛŋ le bachii.
